description:
MapGuide Desktop API for .net. This package includes the FDO (Feature Data Objects) data access libraries. This wraps the x64 unmanaged binaries of mg-desktop.
        
This package replaces the mg-desktop-net40-x64 package. That package still exists and should be considered a legacy package.

Supported Platforms:
- .NET Framework 4.0 and above
title: MapGuide Desktop API (x64)
